A.1.3.2 微分法

$
y=c, y=cx, y=x^n, y=f(x)\cdot g(x), y=\frac{f(x)}{g(x)}, y=a^x (a>0), y=e^x, y=log x
$
の微分.

$
y=c; \frac{dy}{dx}=0
y=cx; \frac{dy}{dx}=c
y=x^n; \frac{dy}{dx}=n\cdot x^{n-1}
y=f(x)\cdot g(x); \frac{dy}{dx}=f'(x)\cdot g(x)+f(x)\cdot g'(x)
y=\frac{f(x)}{g(x)}; \frac{dy}{dx}=\frac{f'(x)\cdot g(x)-f(x)\cdot g'(x)}{\{g(x)\}^2}
y=a^x (a>0); \frac{dy}{dx}= a^x\cdot\log{a}
y=e^x; \frac{dy}{dx}= e^x
y=\log{x}; \frac{dy}{dx}= \frac{1}{x}
$

A.1.3.3積分法


$
f(x) = x^a (a\neq -1),
f(x) = \frac{1}{x},
f(x) = a^x (a>0, a\neq 1),
f(x) = e^x,
a\cdot f(x) \pm b\cdot g(x),
f(x) = \frac{g'(x)}{g(x)}
$
の積分.


[$$]f(x) = x^a (a\neq -1); \int f(x)dx = \frac{x^{a+1}}{a+1}[/$$]
[$$]f(x) = \frac{1}{x}; \int f(x)dx = \log{|x|}[/$$]
[$$]f(x) = a^x (a>0; a\neq 1); \int f(x)dx = \frac{a^x}{\log{a}}[/$$]
[$$]f(x) = e^x; \int f(x)dx = e^x[/$$]
[$$]a\cdot f(x) \pm b\cdot g(x); a\cdot\int f(x)dx \pm b\cdot \int g(x)dx[/$$]
[$$]f(x) = \frac{g'(x)}{g(x)}; \log{|g(x)|}[/$$]

A.1.3.3.1 部分積分の公式

$
\int f'(x)\cdot g(x)dx 
$

$
\int f'(x)\cdot g(x)dx = f(x)\cdot g(x) - \int f(x)\cdot g'(x) dx
$

A.1.3.3.1有用な積分公式
$
\int f(x)\cdot e^{-ax}dx
$

$
\int f(x)\cdot e^{-ax}dx = -e^{-ax}\left\{ \frac{f(x)}{a}+\frac{f'(x)}{a^2}+\frac{f''(x)}{a^3}+\cdots\right\}
$

ガウスの公式

$
\int_{-\infty}^{\infty} e^{-ax^2}
$

$
\int_{-\infty}^{\infty} e^{-ax^2} =
\int_{-\infty}^{\infty} e^{-a(x-b)^2}
=\sqrt{\frac{\pi}{a}}  (a>0)
$

